<BODY LANG="en-US" DIR="LTR">
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><B>How to hack your badge</B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Create an account at
<A HREF="http://lpcxpresso.code-red-tech.com/LPCXpresso/">http://lpcxpresso.code-red-tech.com/LPCXpresso/</A></P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Once your account is activated (email
notification), download the IDE from</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Windows:
<A HREF="http://lpcxpresso.code-red-tech.com/LPCXpresso/Windows">http://lpcxpresso.code-red-tech.com/LPCXpresso/Windows</A></P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Linux:
<A HREF="http://lpcxpresso.code-red-tech.com/LPCXpresso/Linux">http://lpcxpresso.code-red-tech.com/LPCXpresso/Linux</A></P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Activate according to the instructions
on one of the above install pages</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Download
\\Kwartzstation\Arduinator\SVN.ZIP</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Unzip SVN.ZIP to a directory</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">You should have a directory named &ldquo;SVN&rdquo;</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Open LPCXpresso</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Go to File-&gt;Import</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Import General-&gt;Existing Projects</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Browse to SVN, click OK</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">You should now see 3 projects under
&ldquo;Project Explorer&rdquo;</P>
<UL>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Arduinizer</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">CMSISv1p30</P>
</UL>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Ensure the following for all 3 projects</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Build-&gt;Build Configurations-&gt;Set
Active is <B>Release</B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: normal">Click the little
hammer (or Ctrl+b) to build</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: normal">Connect the badge
to your computer via the USB connection. It should show up as a USB
mass storage device</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: normal">Copy the output
.HEX file to the badge</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: normal">Enjoy!</P>
</BODY>
